Open Notepad on Desktop

xcopy <backup folder path which we want to take a backup>* <path of backup file to be saved>\%date:~0,3%\* /Y /Q /S

save the file as backup.bat on Desktop

run the command as Admin


go to Main menu Start --> Task Scheduler-->Create a basic Task-->name is as backup--> next--> Triggers(daily, weekly, monthly) --> Action---> start a program --> browse the backup  batch file ---> Finish

restart the computer and it will takes the backup.
